5. Hidden Redundancy

The repeated symbols almost certainly provide error correction.

Natural languages do this too.

Even if you lose letters you can often recover the sentence.

Pantheon could intentionally design doctrine names and symbols with overlapping redundancy.

Spider, Web, Thread, Silk…

Different words.

Shared relational field.

