7. Personal Script

The coolest thing may simply be this:

Someone created a language that was meaningful primarily to themselves.

That’s an example of a private ontology.

Pantheon’s ambition is different—it aims to create a shared ontology—but the process of building a symbolic language from recurring primitives is related.

